Byte-by-byte Description of file: mcg.dat
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Bytes Format  Units   Label    Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   1- 14  A14    ---     MCG      Morphological Catalog of Galaxies (MCG) number
      15  A1     ---     n_MCG    '*' if there is a note in the
                                    published version
  16- 24  A9     ---    OtherName Catalog number in the NGC or IC
  25- 26  I2     h       RAh      Hours RA, equinox 1950.0
  27- 31  F5.2   min     RAm      Minutes RA, equinox 1950.0
      32  A1     ---     DE-      Sign Dec, equinox 1950.0
  33- 34  I2     deg     DEd      Degrees Dec, equinox 1950.0
  36- 37  I2     arcmin  DEm      Minutes Dec, equinox 1950.0
  39- 43  F5.2   mag     Mag      [6/21]? Photographic Magnitude
  44- 48  F5.1 0.1arcmin MajAxisIn ]0/500]? Diameter of the major axis,
                                    bright inner part
  49- 53  F5.1 0.1arcmin MinAxisIn ]0/500]? Diameter of the minor axis,
                                    bright inner part
  54- 59  F6.1 0.1arcmin MajAxis  ]0/1600]? Diameter of major axis,
                                    entire galaxy
  60- 64  F5.1 0.1arcmin MinAxis  ]0/500]? Diameter of minor axis,
                                    entire galaxy
      65  I1     ---     IntIn    []? [1/6] Intensity of inner region
                                    of the galaxy from 1 (completely black
                                    image) to 6 (image barely visible).
      66  I1     ---     IntOut   [1/6]? Intensity of outer region of the galaxy
      67  A1     ---     Incl     [1-5?] Inclination of the principle Plane
                                         from 1 (face on) to 5 (edge on).
                                         '?'= uncertainty.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Historical Notes:
  * 18-Nov-1994:
    Compared to the "Selected Astronomical Catalogs" Vol. 1 CD-ROM (1992),
    directory "nonstell/galaxies/mcg", the following errors have been
    corrected:
    - Misalignements in records 6734 10857 13382 25010
    - Errors in the "Incl" parameter for records
        3601(MCG+09-11-008) 4053(MCG+09-16-022) 6928(MCG+08-30-002)
        13323(MCG+04-06-049)
    - Error in "MajorAxis" parameter for record 19653(MCG+01-37-012)
  * 22-Oct-1996: Gail L. Schneider (SSDOO/ADC)
    - Error in "MCG" for record 4341 corrected
      For: MCI+09-19-067  Read: MCG+09-19-067
  * 09-Jan-2001: Units of Major/Minor Axises were reported as arcmin --
    but are tenths of arcminutes.

